{
  "title": "Double-Fried, Dense Korean Treacle Jjigae",
  "description": "A low-glycemic Korean dish featuring treacle, inspired by the richness of KFC's double-fried chicken. This dense, sour jjigae is a twist on traditional Korean recipes.",
  "cuisine": "Korean",
